{"tid":1447793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再堵路 再遊行 再多既連燶牆都唔會有用","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:34:30.000Z","uid":115660,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"50e5435d2b13288fd2fa5ba007aba578b979acd1","tid":1447793,"uid":115660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:12:34.000Z","msg":"係  我地對手係政府<br />\n但先要贏警犬<br />\n<br />\n警犬係我地目前最大目標<br />\n我地必需對準目標<br />\n<br />\n點對準？<br />\n要做得到位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">設身處地咁諗<br />\n打份工兩萬蚊<br />\n但如果屋企人隨時會出事<br />\n自己放工跟隨時會出事<br />\n呢份工你仲有無心機打？<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔該啦 唔好再be water 唔好再精神勝利法<br />\n對準目標做該做的事 ok?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">犬舍無腳嫁 唔會走左去 24小時都係到<br />\n有人肯做野未</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">在此希望大家唔好犯法 唔好搞休班犬 唔好搞犬舍</span><br />\n<br />\n否則佢地意志盡失 永無寧日<br />\n我地勝出有望"},{"pid":"cdbeb64748f061ec8d148b0d562b266e68428855","tid":1447793,"uid":115660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:15:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88ec126a4fb9712c75d0c8aea6c981588c82a8d8","tid":1447793,"uid":115660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:15:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4f1d8641ce32da77786c7ec6129e9329fcb87f6","tid":1447793,"uid":270768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o3QAB6g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo3QAB6g.png&h=e58b11d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">此人曾出Post推前線手足去北角<br />\n請提高警惕並善用分不推文回覆</span></span>"},{"pid":"83d0f008eacece7103a4f4944ef8410fbe3b1135","tid":1447793,"uid":115660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:43:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89421b447f13a9f68d0bf15b8faa1dd470e38816","tid":1447793,"uid":115660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"